title: 154: New GM hires, Senior Bowl recap
itunes:title: 154: New GM hires, Senior Bowl recap
description:
After two weeks of traveling to scout the incoming class of football talent Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back in studio to recap what they saw at the Senior Bowl. The duo also give their takes on the new general manager hires across the NFL.
